_header: Helpeth all Holy Church this counsel general
_description: A prayer ‘ffor alle quyke and dede’ — one stanza rhyme royal

Bod549.First Lines:
Helpeth all holy Chirche þis Counseil generallThe holy Pope
                    and byschopes wyt all þe Clergye…
Bod549.Last Lines:
…Prayeth for the sawles godes mercy a bydyngAnd brynggeth vs
                    alle to ȝour blysse euer lastyng
